import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import { StrictMode } from "react"
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom"
import App from "./App"
import "./index.css"

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById("root"))
root.render(
	<StrictMode>
		<BrowserRouter>
			<App className="app" />
		</BrowserRouter>
	</StrictMode>
)
